query:
SELECT DISTINCT p.role, t.nome as tipo_usuario_nome, COUNT(*) as total
FROM permissoes p
LEFT JOIN tipos_usuario t ON p.tipoUsuarioId = t.id
GROUP BY p.role, t.nome
ORDER BY t.nome
